description: Mrs. Alicia Gwynn is cooking up all of Tony’s favorites straight from her family-run gourmet food truck. She’s serving a delicious modern twist on all-American classic cuisine, and with its amazingly tasty farm-to-table quality, this selection is an absolute home run. Gwynn’s Fly Ball Chicken Wing Basket, Pop Fly Pulled Pork Fries, and Base Hit Bratwurst are just a few of the items that will keep you delightedly satisfied all the way through the ninth inning. With all this and much more, you must swing by Gwynn’s Gourmet Food truck for some majorly savory hall-of-fame fare.
name: Gwynn's Gourmet Food Truck
